# Approach
With given condition, friend request can be sent to only people with age greater than ages[i]/2+7 and lesser than ages[i]. 
And map[ages[i]]-map[cond]-1 will give us total no of people that can be friend listed

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(n)

- Space complexity:
