# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Dp will give memory limit exceeded.
so we need to do it by sliding window
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
we need a {  subarray of sum  }  as 
target = total sum - x
then max subarray sum of target 
to get min operation on x

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->   
    O(N)

- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
