1. This sum asks us to find a minimum length subarray (from left end and right end) which equals the traget sum X
2. A small tweak here is, instead we find the maximum length subarray in the given input array whose sum equals (total elements sum - X).
3. So the question boils down the the following sum: https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-size-subarray-sum-equals-k/


